Website Style Guide - Rhiannon Waggener
Overall Formatting
The overall site colors are pink, purple, blue, and green.
The general font-family for the site is New Century Schoolbook with backup fonts Century Gothic and Avanta Garde. The general text size is 1.5em to 3em. 
The overall background color is pink.
Site Header / Branding
The header area font is New Century Schoolbook.
The font-color is purple and blue. With “Rhiannon” in purple and being wavy underlined. “Website” being solid underlined.
The font size is 3em.
Navigation Links
Site navigation uses the font-family Avanta Garde.
The font size is 1.5em.
The webpage navigation links uses padding and margin of 0 auto and margin-left 20px, no padding used.
Content Section
Site Footer
The footer has a background color of no background color on footer.
The font size is 2em.
Content section uses font-family Century Gothic.
The font-color is green, purple, and blue. With “Hi!” in a white border of 0.1em. “Rhiannon” in purple and wavy underlined. “Second year” is bold and dash underlined. “Cascadia College” is blue and bold. “Website” is solid underlined. “Basics of Web Authoring” is italicized.
